<A>__{a single daisy stands in a vase in an empty kitchen.}
<L>__{interior hal's bedroom}
<A>__{oliver fields clicks on the light to the closet. he looks at the rack of his parents' clothes. he begins to put some in a box marked "home", some in a box marked "thrift".}
<L>__{interior hal's bathroom}
<A>__{oliver enters the bathroom and flushes bottle after bottle of pills and liquids down the toilet. next he struggles as he looks over the old toothbrush, hairbrush, all the bottles and tubes besides the sink. he stares for a beat, then throws them all away.}
